            .thumbnail.biografy-box
              img(src='doc/images/ProfilePicture3.jpg', alt='...')
              .caption(style='font-size: 12px')
                p(style="font-size:16px") Let me tell you a Story.
                p(style='text-align:justify; font-size:16px')
                  | Once, I was walking through the forest of my own mind. There, I found a little flower, a story waiting to be told. Suddenly, while I was staring at it, I realized that there wasn’t only one, but millions of them. They were all waiting to be told. I knew I couldn’t just leave them there, so I put as much as I could fit inside a little chest. I decided to let them grow inside it, so one day, all of them can see the light.
                p(style="font-size:16px") My name is Jarys, and Welcome to my Story Box.
          .col-lg-4.popular-post(style='padding: 5px 25px 25px 25px')
